description: Having defected from Russia, Supergirl and Stargirl arrive on the Western front. In Berlin, Batwoman has to learn that she can’t fight every battle, while Zatanna consults her favorite rabbit, the former John Constantine. Meanwhile, Harley and Ivy race across France, taking on every Nazi they encounter.

description: Get a sneak peak into the huge All-New, All-Different Marvel releases launching this December and January! From Spider-Man/Deadpool and Rocket Raccoon & Groot to Squadron Supreme and A-Force, the Marvel Universe just keeps getting more exciting!

Airi wants to make amends with Oto. After being reprimanded by Haruto, she sees the error of her ways. Airi wants Oto to forgive her for distributing the flyers that exposed Oto's secret. She knows it will take time to gain Oto's trust, but she truly wants to be friends. Or does she...?
name: Chapter 17

description: Poor Oto Edogawa can't seem to catch a break. When her wealthy family loses its fortune, she keeps up pretenses at her elite school for the super rich, Eitoku Academy, by supporting herself with a low-wage convenience store job. If the self-appointed guardians of the school and successors of the legendary "F4," the "Correct 5," discover her secret poverty, she'll be expelled! But none of them would ever stoop to shop at a plebeian convenience store...right?
name: Vol. 1

description: Supergirl and Stargirl question their new role with the allied forces. But a sudden attack by an army of undead Tenebrae soon has their attention.
name: Allies Part 5 of 9

description: Themyscira is alive with the sounds of Amazons on the hunt. Will they find their prey before Diana has a chance to rescue the outsider who fell from the sky?
name: Chapter Seven

description: Since the dawn of time, a war has been fought in secret; the inter-species armageddon between Penguins and Possums. A conflict this monumental can only stay in the shadows for so long.
name: Choose a Side

description: Since the dawn of time, the inter-species Armageddon between Penguins and Possums has been fought in secret. With the conflict boiling to the surface, every human on the planet will soon be forced to CHOOSE A SIDE.
name: The Prodigal Prince

description: Peace was at hand. The Possum CHOSEN ONE made a deal with the Penguin Emperor, XIAO, that would have resulted in a ceasefire between the two warring species. It was not to be, thanks to ZOLIN, the ambitious Possum warrior. At the behest of the fractured POSSUM TRIBUNAL, he destroyed the ancient PENGUIN MAUSOLEUM, ending the truce before it began. Now the CHOSEN ONE is imprisoned by the Penguins, and XIAO has declared all-out war on Possums worldwide. However, the greatest enemy to the Possums may lie within...
name: Fractures
